// IntelliJ HTTP Client requests for Lab 5 (includes address field)

### Create a new AddressBook
POST http://localhost:8080/api/addressbooks
Content-Type: application/json

### Add a buddy with address (replace 1 with the actual AB id returned above)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/addressbooks/1/buddies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "phone": "555-1111",
  "address": "100 Main St"
}

### Add another buddy
POST http://localhost:8080/api/addressbooks/1/buddies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob",
  "phone": "555-2222",
  "address": "200 King Rd"
}

### Get AddressBook 1 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/addressbooks/1

### List all buddies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/buddies

### Find buddies by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/buddies?name=Alice

### Remove buddy with id 2 from AddressBook 1 (adjust IDs as returned)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/addressbooks/1/buddies/2

### View Thymeleaf page for AddressBook 1
GET http://localhost:8080/addressbooks/1
